                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2812898/">南国桂藩号莫愁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-11-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">伯林啰嗦了许多被人遗忘的常识。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="97823609">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-97823609" class="vote-count">0</span>
